  <h2>Intro to Programming</h2> 
  <div class="read-more-wrap"><p>A 10 classes course to introduct programming using Processing language with visual appealing  activities. The course is in brazilian portuguese. The final project is a simple game.</p>
    <span class="read-more-target">

      <ul class="read-more-target" >
	<li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLxv-NNCXkBT2TFm6SMsc3_W-PpjkPP10N">Youtube Playlist</a></li>
	<li>Content:
	  <ol>	    	    
	    <li> Introduction (Environment and how a program works)</li>
	    <li> Variable assignment </li>
	    <li> Loops and variable manipulation I </li>
	    <li> Loops and variable manipulation II </li>
	    <li> Conditionals I </li>
	    <li> Conditionals II </li>
	    <li> While command </li>
	    <li> For command </li>
	    <li> Matrix and Boolean I </li>
	    <li> Matrix and Boolean II </li>
	  </ol>
      </ul>
      <div style="text-align:center">
	<figure>
	  <img class="read-more-target" style="align:middle;margin:10px" src="images/intro_prog_game.png"/>
	  <figcaption>Course's final project is a simple tile game. </figcaption>
	</figure>
